<item>
            <title>[LU-12050]  Update ldiskfs kernel patches for Ubuntu 14.04/16.04</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12050</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current Ubuntu ldiskfs kernel patches only work until Kernel 4.4.0-73.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This ticket is about updating the patches to work with Kernel revisions 113 up to 143 (= current as of 2019-03).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Ubuntu 14.04. and 16.04. with Kernel series 4.4.0</environment>
        <key id="55088">LU-12050</key>
            <summary> Update ldiskfs kernel patches for Ubuntu 14.04/16.04</summary>
